Sorry to take a long. Updated tests to meet NumPy changes. 

One remaining error in Azure is caused by network connection which looks unrelated to the change.
Seems to be a datetime failure: https://travis-ci.org/pandas-dev/pandas/jobs/482209044#L2539

This is spitting out, but *only* on the comparison on the expected result. I think these tests prob need if its a datetimelike type, coerce to i8, do the op, coerce back.

